What people think about our work</h2></div></div></section><section id="id-t0V71XaQ" class="section slider pt-0 pt-lg-0 pb-120 pb-lg-160 " ><div  class="container     "><div  class="    swiper uq-slider  slide-small blur overflow-visible" ><div  class="    swiper-wrapper" ><div  class="    swiper-slide" ><div  class="    card card-offset-sm shadow radius-lg" ><div  class="    card-body" ><p class=" card-text ff-primary mb-0">I am super happy with the entire process and the result of the renovations to my home. They have creative ideas and adapt to the budget while always maintaining maximum quality.</p></div><div  class="    card-footer" ><p class=" footer-title fw-bold ff-secondary mb-0">Gemma</p></div></div></div><div  class="    swiper-slide" ><div  class="    card card-offset-sm shadow radius-lg" ><div  class="    card-body" ><p class=" card-text ff-primary mb-0">We have worked several times with Calacatta, not only for interior design but also for space redistribution, installation of supplies, etc... and it has always been a great experience. The professionalism and excellent taste of both Cecilia and Inés, the personalized attention and the search for the best solutions for our needs and budget. We look forward to having another project on hand to work with them again.</p></div><div  class="    card-footer" ><p class=" footer-title fw-bold ff-secondary mb-0">Jessica & Francisco</p></div></div></div><div  class="    swiper-slide" ><div  class="    card card-offset-sm shadow radius-lg" ><div  class="    card-body" ><p class=" card-text ff-primary mb-0">I had always dreamed of a beautiful, cozy, and family-friendly home. And Calacatta perfectly captured my essence. Working with Inés and Ceci was very easy and fun; we chose every last detail and the result was spectacular. They left me with a magazine-worthy home. Their professionalism and expertise made everything very easy. I would choose them again a thousand times over!</p></div><div  class="    card-footer" ><p class=" footer-title fw-bold ff-secondary mb-0">Anna & Álvaro</p></div></div></div><div  class="    swiper-slide" ><div  class="    card card-offset-sm shadow radius-lg" ><div  class="    card-body" ><p class=" card-text ff-primary mb-0">
The Calacatta team forms a great team and it shows when working with them. They are great professionals and completely adjust to the needs of each person with the budget, always finding stylish solutions for EVERYTHING. Every time I have worked with them, I have been delighted, turning their renovations into more than a home, into a true sanctuary.</p></div><div  class="    card-footer" ><p class=" footer-title fw-bold ff-secondary mb-0">Montse & Óscar</p></div></div></div><div  class="    swiper-slide" ><div  class="    card card-offset-sm shadow radius-lg" ><div  class="    card-body" ><p class=" card-text ff-primary mb-0">The Calacatta team not only left us with a beautiful house but also created a home for us! They have an exquisite taste, adapt to your needs, have a great list of suppliers, and the team that carried out the work has been excellent! Dedicated, willing to solve any type of problems, and very polite.The experience with Calacatta has been magnificent and I can only say wonderful things about Inés and Ceci! They put love into the project, propose tailor-made solutions, and I have to say that the apartment looks BEAUTIFUL! Thank you for your magnificent work and dedication!!!</p></div><div  class="    card-footer" ><p class=" footer-title fw-bold ff-secondary mb-0">Sofía & Nacho</p></div></div></div></div><div class="swiper-button-next">
